N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6055.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of this Part is to establish procedures
providing for participation in the Statewide Central Register for Missing

Children (hereinafter referred to as the Register). Notes
